video_title: One of the most dangerous beliefs in a relationship
transcript:
as I've said before one of the most
dangerous relationship beliefs is the
belief that in your relationship you are
finally free to be yourself warts and
all in point of fact a relationship like
a job is a privilege and one you have to
constantly earn a new by providing
sufficient value it is a privilege to be
a husband and a privilege to be a wife
it is a privilege to be a boyfriend and
a privilege to be a girlfriend
relationships are roles and we don't
ever get to stop playing
